It is the invisible expiry date of value in nature-based systems.


Ignored by markets. Omitted from forecasts. And now exposed.


Biocenescence is

The depreciation curve of life itself.

The unpriced terminus of biological utility.

The failure point hiding in every natural supply chain. This is not Decay.

This is the terminal threshold of productivity.

